quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,Ndahiriye ku (bamalayika) bashikanuza (roho z’abahakanyi) n’ubukana buhambaye
  79,2,No ku (bamalayika) bakuramo (roho z’abemeramana) bitonze
  79,3,No ku (bamalayika) bogoga ikirere bihuta (batwaye izo roho)
  79,4,No ku (bamalayika) bihutana (ubutumwa babuzaniye intumwa za Allah ku isi)
  79,5,No ku (bamalayika) bashyira mu bikorwa ibyo bategetswe
  79,6,"Umunsi (impanda ya mbere izavuzwa), maze isi n’imisozi bigatigita bikabije (buri kiremwa kigapfa)"
  79,7,(Umutingito wa mbere) uzakurikirwa n’undi mutingito (maze buri kiremwa kizuke)
  79,8,Uwo munsi imitima (ya bamwe) izaba ifite ubwoba n’agahinda
  79,9,Ndetse n’indoro yabo izaba yaciye bugufi (isuzuguritse)
  79,10,"Bazavuga bati \"Ese mu by’ukuri, tuzasubizwa mu buzima (bwacu bwo ku isi) twahozemo"
  79,11,Na nyuma y’uko tubaye amagufa ashangutse
  79,12,"Baravuga bati \"Uko kugaruka kwacu (ku isi twifuza) kwaba ari igihombo"
  79,13,(Ubwo impanda izavuzwa bwa kabiri) bizaba ari urusaku rumwe
  79,14,Icyo gihe bazisanga imusozi (bongeye kuba bazima nyuma yo gupfa)
  79,15,Ese inkuru ya Musa yakugezeho
  79,16,Ubwo Nyagasani we yamuhamagaraga mu kibaya gitagatifu cya Tuwa (agira ati)
  79,17,Jya kwa Farawo kuko rwose yigometse
  79,18,"Umubwire uti \"Ese ushobora kwiyeza (ukareka icyaha cy’ubuhakanyi, ukaba umwemeramana)"
  79,19,Nkakuyobora kwa Nyagasani wawe kugira ngo umutinye
  79,20,Nuko (Musa) amwereka igitangaza gihambaye
  79,21,Ariko (Farawo) yarahinyuye aranigomeka
  79,22,Maze atera umugongo akataza (ashishikariza abantu be kudakurikira Musa)
  79,23,"Nuko akoranya (abantu be), avuga mu ijwi riranguruye"
  79,24,"Agira ati \"Ni njye nyagasani wanyu w’ikirenga"
  79,25,"Bityo, Allah amuhanira icyaha cya nyuma (cyo kuvuga ko ari we nyagasani w’ikirenga) n’icya mbere (cyo kuba yarabwiye ibyegera bye ko atazi ko bafite indi mana itari we)"
  79,26,"Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo isomo kuri buri wese utinya Allah"